# Mockup Analysis — Before First Line of Code

**Firma:** HorosCode · **Produkt:** HorosCloud

**Never write AXAML until analysis is complete.**

## Extraction Checklist

| Category | Extract | Document in |
|----------|---------|-------------|
| Layout | Root frame size, regions, flex/grid structure | Task comment / mini-plan |
| Grid | Columns, rows, `*` vs fixed, alignment | Region notes |
| Spacing | Padding, margin, gap between siblings | Token candidates |
| Radius | Corner radius per element | `design-memory.md` if new |
| Typography | Font, size, weight, line-height, color | Token candidates |
| Colors | BG, surface, text, border, accent, states | `design-memory.md` if new |
| Components | Buttons, inputs, nav, cards, icons | Component inventory |

## Figma MCP (preferred)

```text
1. GetMcpTools → Figma server
2. Load frame hierarchy + auto-layout
3. Export spacing/typography/color per node
4. Mark regions for incremental workflow
```

## Screenshot Fallback

```text
1. Record viewport size (e.g. 1440×900)
2. Draw region boundaries manually
3. Measure spacing with grid overlay
4. Expect ~70–85% start parity — plan extra review rounds
```

## Analysis Output Template

```markdown
## Mockup Analysis — [Frame Name]

**Viewport:** 1440×900 · **Theme:** Dark

### Regions
1. Header — 1440×56, fixed top
2. Sidebar — 240×844, left
3. Content — 1200×844, scroll

### New Tokens Needed
| Key | Value | Usage |
|-----|-------|-------|
| SpacingHeaderX | 24px | Header horizontal padding |

### Components
- Primary CTA button (amber, 40px height)
- Nav item with active state (left border accent)
```

## Never

- **Never** start coding with "I'll figure out spacing later"
- **Never** guess colors — measure or read from Figma
- **Never** skip region decomposition (`01-workflow`)

